node.text:
HP, in partnership with @sxsw, convened the first virtual summit of community leaders working to advance digital equity and increase access to education, healthcare, and economic opportunity. Together, we started an important dialogue, listening and learning to spark change.

Each conversation was designed to elevate the voices of Black, Indigenous, and People of Color leaders who are advancing digital equity within their own communities. Below are some of our key takeaways from the event, along with resources and upcoming gatherings to keep the conversation going.

To watch the full event, please visit the link in bio.

#digitalequity, #education, #hybridlearning, #healthcare, #telehealth, #telemedicine, #economicopportunity, #digitaldivide

node.text: See the future through the eyes of real life changemakers Tiana Day, Jacqueline Azah, Fionn Ferreira and Kavya Kopparapu. Whether you want to reform education, clean up the ocean, reverse climate change or become the next leader of your country, your aspirations have no limits. HP’s new powerful PCs won’t hold you back, so you can focus on every dream in the making. [link in bio]

node.text:
HP, in partnership with @sxsw, convened the first virtual summit of community leaders working to advance digital equity and increase access to education, healthcare, and economic opportunity. Together, we started an important dialogue, listening and learning to spark change.

Each conversation was designed to elevate the voices of Black, Indigenous, and People of Color leaders who are advancing digital equity within their own communities. Below are some of our key takeaways from the event, along with resources and upcoming gatherings to keep the conversation going.

To watch the full event, please visit the link in bio.

#digitalequity, #education, #hybridlearning, #healthcare, #telehealth, #telemedicine, #economicopportunity, #digitaldivide

node.text:
Earlier this year, HP pledged to accelerate digital equity for 150 million people by 2030. But what, in fact, does digital equity mean, and what will it take to get there? 
See the story linked in bio and learn why access to technology, digital skills, and tools can make a world of difference when it comes to people's opportunities for education, healthcare, and higher-earning careers.
